# 📌 Smart Bookmark CRUD Application

A full-stack Bookmark Manager built entirely using Python.

This application allows users to:
- Add a bookmark
- View all bookmarks
- Update a bookmark
- Delete a bookmark

Built using:
- Python
- Streamlit (Frontend + Backend)
- SQLite (Database)

---

